First we need nvm installed on our cluster for that run the following command.
curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.33.2/install.sh | bash

Then to install node run the following command.
nvm install node

To install the packages required for the project to run. Run the following command
npm install.

Start the server my writting startChord.sh N. Where N will be number of nodes.

